	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi all,<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;   On my way to level 20, I was all excited about getting rid of my damage cap to see what damage I could do with my Frozen Long Sword. I was going 15 max damage, and then I hit 20 that didn't change.<br><br>     Now I'm 21 and have also bought a PGT. I proc an extra 35 strength at times, yet still my damage does not increase. Am I still afflicted with a damage cap, or is it simply hopeless for a bard to increase damage through strength?<br><br>    Thanks<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Benolan Bladenote<br>Bard of the 39th song</td></tr>
